title: Trisha & Ethan Do Goat Yoga & Carpool Karaoke - Frenemies #11
description: On this episode of Frenemies Trisha & Ethan hit up some goat yoga, and on the way home belt some tunes together in the car. Afterward Trisha has a big announcement to share...
